OL,3,CEdinburgh Trams staff back strike
OL,4,Caction over lack of breaks
OL,6,FWorkers on Edinburgh's tram network
OL,7,Fhave backed strike action in a dispute
OL,8,Fover a lack of toilet breaks.
OL,10,FThe union Unite said late running
OL,11,Fservices mean drivers are unable to
OL,12,Ftake a break ahead of their next
OL,13,Fdeparture, which has led to health
OL,14,Fissues among members.
OL,16,FUnite said 160 staff could strike
OL,17,Fafter a ballot was backed by more than
OL,18,F90% of its members.
