OL,3,CEdinburgh Trams staff back strike
OL,4,Caction over lack of breaks
OL,6,FSharon Graham, general secretary of
OL,7,FUnite, said: "Unite's Edinburgh tram
OL,8,Fworkers have emphatically backed
OL,9,Fstrike action in order to tackle head-
OL,10,Fon the unacceptable health and safety
OL,11,Fsituation they face.
OL,13,F"They should not be in this situation
OL,14,Fbecause Edinburgh Trams should be
OL,15,Fimplementing measures to ensure our
OL,16,Fmembers get their comfort breaks.
OL,18,F"We will back our tram membership all
OL,19,Fthe way in the fight for decent
OL,20,Fworkplace conditions."
