OL,3,CEdinburgh Trams staff back strike
OL,4,Caction over lack of breaks
OL,6,FLyn Turner, an industrial officer at
OL,7,Fthe union, added: "Edinburgh's tram
OL,8,Fworkers are being forced into taking
OL,9,Fstrike action.
OL,11,F"This is mismanagement plain and
OL,12,Fsimple, and it is having unacceptable
OL,13,Fconsequences for our members.
OL,15,F"Unite wants to resolve this through
OL,16,Fnegotiation but we are running out of
OL,17,Ftrack before strike action takes
OL,18,Fplace. If this happens, then Edinburgh
OL,19,FTrams will be solely to blame for any
OL,20,Fdisruption. Management has one more
OL,21,Fchance."
